</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
20:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1222742' id='t-1222742'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
20:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1223909' id='t-1223909'>And jumping monks of Tibet.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
20:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1225393' id='t-1225393'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
20:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1227000' id='t-1227000'>Flying monks.</span>
</span>
</p>
